<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="17" type="type material">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="17">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="17">
Holotype in MCZ: male, with label &quot; MCZ, MEXICO: TABASCO: 2.4 km E of Teapa, Grutas de Cocona, ca. 
<geoCoordinate degrees="17" direction="north" minutes="33" orientation="latitude" precision="925" value="17.55">17°33'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="92" direction="west" minutes="56" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="-92.933334">92°56'W</geoCoordinate>
7 July 1983 W.Maddison 83-089 forested steep slope, ca. 250 ft. el.&quot;. The recorded latitude is likely incorrect; the specimen was collected near the entrance to the Grutas, which is at ca. 
<geoCoordinate degrees="17.564" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="55" value="17.564">17.564N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="92.929" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="55" value="-92.929">92.929W</geoCoordinate>
.
</paragraph>
